     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Technical Working Group established under State Commitee on Construction and Architecture on revision of SNiP; 
2. New SNiP developed and approved by the Government on simplifying construction standards for affordable waste and sanitation infrastructure building in rural areas;
3. Developed and approved the Guideline on using the new SNIP;
4. Law on Drinking Water and wastewater developed and approved by the Government of Tajikistan;
5. Organized and conducted the national round table and presented the final version of the new Law on drinking water and wastewater to all key stakeholders and development partners; 
6. Developed 1 analysis on financial contribution of GoT and development partners in water and sanitation sector and presented to all key stakeholders and development partners within the framework of Water Sector Reform Programme; 
7. 4 Policy briefs developed and published on (a) Tariff setting, (b) Taxation of drinking water sector (c) Construction Norms and Standards of rural drinking water supply systems and (d) Rural water supply and sanitation reform of the drinking water sector;</narrative>
      </comment>
